<inglise> Whereas, because of the specific and particularly difficult working and living conditions on board fishing vessels, the incidence of fatal accidents among workers engaged in sea fishing is very high; </inglise>
<eesti> spetsiifiliste ja eriti raskete t&ouml;&ouml;- ja elutingimuste t&otilde;ttu kalalaeva pardal on surmaga l&otilde;ppenud &otilde;nnetuste hulk merekalap&uuml;&uuml;giga tegelevate t&ouml;&ouml;tajate hulgas v&auml;ga suur; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, on 15 April 1988, the European Parliament adopted a resolution recognizing the importance of the preventive aspects of safety at work on board fishing vessels; </inglise>
<eesti> 15. aprillil 1988 v&otilde;ttis Euroopa Parlament vastu resolutsiooni, milles tunnistati kalalaeva pardal t&ouml;&ouml;ohutust tagavate ennetavate tegurite t&auml;htsust; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, for the safety and health of the workers concerned, prominence should be given to locating fishing vessels in an emergency, particularly through the use of new technologies; </inglise>
