<eesti> Umbreelinguid v&otilde;i muid piirdeid, mis hoiavad inimesi &uuml;le parda kukkumast, peab hoidma etten&auml;htud seisundis. </eesti>
<inglise> Bulwarks must be fitted with freeing ports or other similar devices to enable water to drain away quickly. </inglise>
<eesti> Umbreelingutes peavad olema tormiluugid v&otilde;i muud samalaadsed seadmed, mis v&otilde;imaldavad vee kiire &auml;ravoolu. </eesti>
<inglise> 11.5. </inglise>
<eesti> 11.5. </eesti>
<inglise> On stern trawlers with ramps, the ramp must be fitted with a gate or other means of securing it of the same height as the bulwarks or other adjacent means, to protect workers from the risk of falling into the ramp. </inglise>
