<inglise> 13.1. </inglise>
<eesti> 13.1. </eesti>
<inglise> The workers' living quarters, where they exist, must be such as to minimize noise, vibration, the effects of motion and acceleration, and unpleasant odours from other parts of the vessel. </inglise>
