<inglise> 14. </inglise>
<eesti> 14. </eesti>
<inglise> Sanitary facilities </inglise>
<eesti> Sanitaars&otilde;lmed </eesti>
<inglise> On vessels with living quarters, toilets, wash-basins and, if possible, a shower must be installed and the respective areas must be properly ventilated. </inglise>
